comment.body:
To support testing Psalm 5 properly I needed to update some other dev dependencies. To ensure there aren't any problems continuing to test this plugin in CI I will release a new version, 2.0.0, for Psalm 5 support. Users of Psalm 4 should stay on the 1.0.0 release.

A new PR will handle the necessary upgrades and this PR is no longer necessary.
